name: Droid Racks
Lore: 'The Trade Federation utilizes such efficient methods of droid deployment that it is rumored even they do not know exactly how many battle druids are in circulation',
Text: 'Use 4 Force to deploy on table. If your battle droid was just lost, may place it here. During your control phase, may use 2 Force (1 Force if your piloted MTT on table) to take any battle droid from here into hand. (Immune to Alter.)',
